{"tid":755222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大連跨海大橋橋墩現裂縫　設計者：正常伸縮縫","createTime":"2018-07-25T04:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T06:24:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":30,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":123,"replies":[{"pid":"dbc14788d6759f681bd9ffd4f07a885728c7dadc","tid":755222,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180725/s00004/19d5f728d82ea3afe7c9e84118e44754.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180725%2Fs00004%2F19d5f728d82ea3afe7c9e84118e44754.jpg&h=9278c45f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地基建工程屢有隱憂，有網民近日於遼寧大連星海灣一座跨海大橋橋墩上，發現一道極明顯裂縫，讓人憂慮工程質量。事件發酵後，設計者及大橋管理方先後接受傳媒訪問，指裂縫是正常的伸縮縫設計，用作抵禦大橋因冷縮熱脹而變形。<br />\n<br />\n設計者應旭永稱，有關裂縫術語為伸縮縫。用以防止橋樑結構因溫度變形而被破壞的設計，是任何橋樑都需要的結構。他又稱，因星海灣大橋有雙層設計，墩樑連接有別於一般橋樑，加上施工質素參差，導致伸縮縫不平整，從而給人橋體混凝土破裂的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n至於身為大橋管理方的星海灣開發建設管理中心，他們稱昨日（24日）早上已派員修補裂縫理，同時全面檢查大橋所有橋墩及相應的設施查，保證橋體美觀效果，又承諾今後將增派人員巡查大橋，並定期邀請專家檢測。<br />\n<br />\n星海灣跨海大橋2015年10月開通，全長6公里，是東北地區最長的跨海大橋工程，也是中國首座海上地錨懸索式跨海大橋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180725/s00004/1532488049734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180725%2Fs00004%2F1532488049734&d=6VBb3GZXc6PsEmgOQRdGZ4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=8c8e2bb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180725%2Fs00004%2F1532488049734&h=ef86d858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180725/s00004/1532488049734</a>"},{"pid":"c51a9c53fd1e5cf0b9d372d67cb468f45850c8b7","tid":755222,"uid":57308,"like":181,"dislike":2,"score":179,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"有毒氣體無害"},{"pid":"fa19e80cd70f345d6c08094c23f869ca818fee01","tid":755222,"uid":39628,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:48:43.000Z","msg":"偷工減料, 梗係正常啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588b5b9cdf0444d476ae9a2572d0b8bdc24f49a3","tid":755222,"uid":7125,"like":19,"dislike":43,"score":-24,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"唔想炒車 有無engine界朋友入黎講下"},{"pid":"e356ff7c6a74a80f09760369ddf3e2f6bf8445a3","tid":755222,"uid":132189,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:54:33.000Z","msg":"會唔會裂得咁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f106eb918fffb7b8bcaadcf8ac3fec29b330842e","tid":755222,"uid":55597,"like":123,"dislike":11,"score":112,"quote":{"pid":"588b5b9cdf0444d476ae9a2572d0b8bdc24f49a3","tid":755222,"uid":7125,"like":19,"dislike":43,"score":-24,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"唔想炒車 有無engine界朋友入黎講下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:56:12.000Z","msg":"驚炒車就唔好問"},{"pid":"287d41937c4177e40cb9f1da01d40578d68cc558","tid":755222,"uid":192052,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"點睇都唔會裂得咁有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港咁多橋又唔見裂成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa085a9c845430c1dca0d4149d9631905625a34c","tid":755222,"uid":71768,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:59:14.000Z","msg":"同我預計既一樣 不論裂縫既長度 深度 闊度 位置都同我計算既差不多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一次預計裂會斷橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f3dbd79a540a79cfe261332634464054d7fbc5","tid":755222,"uid":66242,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:59:38.000Z","msg":"而家熱縮冷脹？"},{"pid":"d0d21fb5d4e9b1716a7e579177baf4b717b83244","tid":755222,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:00:12.000Z",